WEBVTT

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:02.341
Tere tulemast tagasi!

00:00:02.341 --> 00:00:04.575
Eelmine kord nägid sa fork-käsklusi.

00:00:04.575 --> 00:00:05.469
Nüüd vaatame,

00:00:05.469 --> 00:00:07.256
mida need tegelikult tähendavad:

00:00:07.256 --> 00:00:08.597
reaalajas töötav andmebaasirakendus,

00:00:08.597 --> 00:00:09.491
kopeeritud sekunditega,

00:00:09.491 --> 00:00:10.384
muudetav vabalt,

00:00:10.384 --> 00:00:13.066
samal ajal kui originaal ei märka

00:00:13.066 --> 00:00:13.513
midagi.

00:00:14.292 --> 00:00:16.088
Siin on olukord:

00:00:16.088 --> 00:00:19.082
päris PostgreSQL koos pgAdmin liidesega

00:00:19.082 --> 00:00:19.681
peal,

00:00:19.681 --> 00:00:20.879
otseülekandes serveris.

00:00:20.879 --> 00:00:23.873
Fork on hetkeliselt loodud copy-on-write

00:00:23.873 --> 00:00:25.669
kaksik kõigest sellest.

00:00:25.669 --> 00:00:27.466
Sünnihetkel samad andmed,

00:00:27.466 --> 00:00:29.861
pärast täiesti eraldi elud.

00:00:33.126 --> 00:00:34.778
Meet the app:

00:00:34.778 --> 00:00:35.328
demo-pgadmin,

00:00:35.328 --> 00:00:38.081
a PostgreSQL with a pgAdmin

00:00:38.081 --> 00:00:38.632
interface,

00:00:38.632 --> 00:00:40.284
mounted and running.

00:00:43.284 --> 00:00:44.412
Üks reaalajas repo.

00:00:44.412 --> 00:00:45.164
Kloonime selle.

00:00:45.673 --> 00:00:48.672
See on originaal,

00:00:48.672 --> 00:00:49.671
brauseris.

00:00:49.671 --> 00:00:52.670
pgAdmin küsib sisselogimist,

00:00:52.670 --> 00:00:55.669
sest see on

00:00:55.669 --> 00:00:58.668
tootmiskoopia ja tootmine

00:00:58.668 --> 00:01:00.667
jääb kaitstuks.

00:01:19.340 --> 00:01:20.161
Fork it.

00:01:20.161 --> 00:01:23.035
The copy-on-write clone takes seconds regardless of

00:01:23.035 --> 00:01:23.446
size;

00:01:23.446 --> 00:01:26.321
detach returns as soon as the containers

00:01:26.321 --> 00:01:26.731
start,

00:01:26.731 --> 00:01:29.606
while health checks continue in the background.

00:01:29.708 --> 00:01:30.992
Forkitud ja käivitub.

00:01:30.992 --> 00:01:32.276
Andmeid ei kopeeritud,

00:01:32.276 --> 00:01:33.132
need jagati,

00:01:33.132 --> 00:01:35.272
kuni üks pool neid muudab.

00:01:38.522 --> 00:01:41.460
Ja siin on fork'i pgAdmin.

00:01:41.460 --> 00:01:43.224
Seekord sisselogimist pole:

00:01:43.224 --> 00:01:45.575
fork'id on ühekordsed sandbox'id,

00:01:45.575 --> 00:01:48.513
nii et värav astub kõrvale.

00:01:48.513 --> 00:01:49.689
Samad tabelid,

00:01:49.689 --> 00:01:50.865
samad read,

00:01:50.865 --> 00:01:52.628
aga oma universum.

00:02:30.388 --> 00:02:31.509
Two repositories now:

00:02:31.509 --> 00:02:33.376
the original and the experiment,

00:02:33.376 --> 00:02:35.242
each with its own containers,

00:02:35.242 --> 00:02:35.616
network,

00:02:35.616 --> 00:02:36.736
and disk view.

00:02:39.736 --> 00:02:41.032
Sama masin,

00:02:41.032 --> 00:02:42.975
kaks isoleeritud maailma.

00:02:46.288 --> 00:02:47.245
Done experimenting?

00:02:47.245 --> 00:02:48.681
Delete the fork.

00:02:48.681 --> 00:02:50.116
Seconds to create,

00:02:50.116 --> 00:02:52.987
seconds to throw away — the

00:02:52.987 --> 00:02:55.379
original never knew it existed.

00:02:58.379 --> 00:02:58.840
Kadunud.

00:02:58.840 --> 00:03:01.148
Originaal teenis kogu selle aja.

00:03:01.951 --> 00:03:04.160
Nii et tee fork'e vabalt,

00:03:04.160 --> 00:03:05.927
tootmine ei saa viga.

00:03:05.927 --> 00:03:07.252
Järgmisena vaatame saladusi,

00:03:07.252 --> 00:03:08.577
seda üht asja,

00:03:08.577 --> 00:03:11.227
mida sinu fork'id tahtlikult ei päri.

00:03:11.227 --> 00:03:11.669
Kohtumiseni!
